to finish the padding problem in a page
#root ,html{
 width: 100%;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}
so you can make the bullets inside next to the text
li{
   list-style-position: inside;
}

change the bullet color in lists
li::marker{
  for colors:  color:rgb(0, 216, 255);
for sizes : front-siz:20px
}


{
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: right 65%;  to control both x and y
    background-position-x: right; just x
    background-position-y: 65%; just y
}


if you use flex box an element might shrink or become smaller 
here is how to solve it:
img.main-image-container {
 flex-shrink: 0;
}

